     <int-org-section id="IOM.CASEE.146" sllink="SLSDOC" slsdocrf="INT-ORG-SECTREF">
          <heading>Finance</heading>
          <p id="IOM.CASEE.133">IOM's proposed operational budget for 2024 totalled US&#160;$1,839m., while the proposed administrative budget for that year was $77.1m. A Migration Emergency Funding Mechanism approved in December 2011 by the IOM Council facilitates the immediate provision of assistance following a natural disaster or emergency conflict situation, and in particular to cover the cost of international transport for those affected.</p>
